faq-one-title: How many type of payment method supported?
faq-one-content: You can pay cash on delivery or pay online via stripe.
faq-three-title: How much time it will take to deliver order?
faq-three-content: Normally it takes 3 days but also depends upon order placing, like if you place order from multiple shop then it will take 2 to 3 days extra to deliver order.
faq-four-content: Yes, you have to create a seller account. once our register as a seller then your administrator will look into your info and approve your seller.
